COMMON OF APOSTLES
HYMN
Sing joyfully of the friends of God,
Th eir message has resounded throughout the land,
Th eir words to the ends of the earth,
Th ey have followed Christ from the beginning.
Th ey have been victorious in the great trial,
Th ey have washed their robes in the Blood of the Lamb,
Th ey have put on the radiant garment,
Th e Angels acclaim them, the Powers bow down before them.
Th e Apostles, through their faith, have defeated the kingdoms,
Th ey have become the foundations of the Church,
In her, their doctrine shines by means of Christ
As the moon shines by means of the sun.
O Christ, Savior of the world
Save your Church, the sheep of your pasture,
With the Father and the Most Holy Spirit
May you be praised for ever and ever. Amen.
