FIRST VESPERS
PSALMODY
ps 115 ant Adv - ps 110 ant Lent - ps 144 ant OT - NT 4
READING Acts 2:42-45 Th e
brethren devoted themselves to the apostles’
teaching and fellowship, to the breaking of bread and the prayers.
And fear came upon every soul; and many wonders and signs were
done through the apostles. And all who believed were together
and had all things in common; and they sold their possessions and
goods and distributed them to all, as any had need.
MAGNIFICAT :
You did not choose me, but I chose you to go forth and
bear fruit that will last forever.
